vote.title: Authorize an amendment to Resolution No. 16-1733, previously approved on October 26, 2016, to redirect special event parking revenue and accept and deposit daily parking revenue generated by the Farmers Market Public Parking Garage - Estimated Revenue:  Farmers Market TIF District Fund $53,154.00 annually
